FBIS4-14269 "drnes083_p_94002" FBIS-NES-94-083 Daily Report 28 Apr 1994 SOUTH ASIA Afghanistan Fighting in Baghlan Province Continues Fighting in Baghlan Province Continues LD2804204894 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran First Program Network in Persian 1930 GMT 28 Apr 94 LD2804204894 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran First Program Network Persian BFN [Text] In an interview with IRNA on Thursday, a spokesman for the Afghan Hezb-e Eslami said: Fighting between the forces of the Afghan Islamic Revolution Coordination Council and the forces loyal to the president of that country in Baghlan Province is sill continuing. He said that a sector has been surrounded by the opposition forces and important roads leading to that area have fallen into the hands of the forces of the Coordination Council.
